&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üóìÔ∏è Rachel Andrew rounds up &lt;a href="https://frontendfoc.us/link/180245/rss" style=" color: #D94306; font-weight: 600;"&gt;web platform updates from the past month&lt;/a&gt;, including Anchor Positioning and the Navigation API reaching Baseline status.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ü™ê Popular content site framework &lt;a href="https://frontendfoc.us/link/180216/rss" style=" color: #D94306; font-weight: 600;"&gt;Astro 5.17 is now available&lt;/a&gt;, introducing partitioned cookies, new image optimization upgrades, and more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üìã &lt;a href="https://frontendfoc.us/link/180217/rss" style=" color: #D94306; font-weight: 600;"&gt;Short-lived (six-day) and IP address certificates are now generally available&lt;/a&gt; from Let‚Äôs Encrypt.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üß≠ &lt;a href="https://frontendfoc.us/link/180218/rss" style=" color: #D94306; font-weight: 600;"&gt;Here are the release notes&lt;/a&gt; for Safari Technology Preview 236 ‚Äî¬†it adds math function support to the &lt;code&gt;sizes&lt;/code&gt; attribute of &lt;code&gt;img&lt;/code&gt; elements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;‚ú® Fran√ßois Beaufort shares &lt;a href="https://frontendfoc.us/link/180219/rss" style=" color: #D94306; font-weight: 600;"&gt;what's new in WebGPU in Chrome 145.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
