&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üîé Google has &lt;a href="https://frontendfoc.us/link/179852/rss" style=" color: #D94306; font-weight: 600;"&gt;announced a restructuring its Programmable Search Engine (PSE) offerings&lt;/a&gt;, providing more specialized tools for site exploration, enterprise AI search, and full web indexing.&lt;/p&gt;
