&lt;p&gt;üñºÔ∏è Support for the JPEG-XL image format has been on &lt;a href="https://frontendfoc.us/link/179856/rss" style=" color: #D94306; font-weight: 600;"&gt;something of a journey&lt;/a&gt;, but its fortunes are seemingly &lt;a href="https://frontendfoc.us/link/179857/rss" style=" color: #D94306; font-weight: 600;"&gt;turning around&lt;/a&gt;, slowly.&lt;/p&gt;
