&lt;p&gt;üñºÔ∏è JPEG XL support has been &lt;a href="https://frontendfoc.us/link/179175/rss" style=" color: #D94306; font-weight: 600;"&gt;merged into Chromium&lt;/a&gt; (and is showing up in Canary). Enable via: &lt;code&gt;chrome://flags/#enable-jxl-image-format&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
